custom_fields.label: Deduct On
custom_fields.name: Salary Structure Assignment-deduct_on
custom_fields.options:
Transport Deduct on 15th Day
Transport Deduct on 30th Day
Transport Deduct on 15th and 30th Day

custom_fields.description:
The amount to be entered must be proportional to the option selected in Deduct On:

• If you select Transport Deduct on 15th Day or Transport Deduct on 30th Day, the full amount will be deducted on that date.

• If you select Transport Deduct on 15th and 30th Day, the entered amount will be split in two, with half deducted on each payday.
